title: Bobby and Eddie Make A Bet About a Rolling Stones Concert + Abby Shares What Might Be The Final Update on Firefighter Situation + Names Missing From The Country Song!
itunes:title: Bobby and Eddie Make A Bet About a Rolling Stones Concert + Abby Shares What Might Be The Final Update on Firefighter Situation + Names Missing From The Country Song!
description:
Eddie was so sure that he and Bobby went to a Rolling Stones concert together years ago. Bobby says there is no chance he went because he would remember. Bobby and Eddie make a bet and we find out if it’s true or not. Bobby talks to Phone Screener Abby and the firefighter texting situation. He reads emails from listeners who have questions and concerts for her. We play the Names Missing from The Country Song game.
